  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `dailyBriefingRegistration.ts` and the local `types.ts` to map current factory signature.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `calendarRegistration.ts` as the precedent shape.</step>
    <step order="3">Add `loadNotificationContext?: () =&gt; Promise&lt;NarrateRequest | null&gt;` to the factory options interface; thread it through the registration to wherever the briefing fetch is initiated.</step>
    <step order="4">When the option is omitted, behavior MUST match current empty-payload contract (BFF returns empty bullets; UI renders empty state).</step>
    <step order="5">When provided, the value is invoked once per briefing fetch and the result is the NarrateRequest payload posted to BFF `/narrate`.</step>
    <step order="6">Run TypeScript build for the local Spaarke.UI.Components package; confirm no type errors.</step>
