  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">Given no `loadNotificationContext` provided, when the registration is mounted, then BFF `/narrate` is called with an empty/default payload and the UI renders empty state (FR-01 default branch).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Given `loadNotificationContext` is provided, when the registration mounts and fetches, then the function is invoked and its result is used as the BFF `/narrate` request body.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">TypeScript build passes with no new errors or warnings.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

